sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Browser as Browser (Client)
    participant Server as Server (Better Auth)
    participant Google as Google OAuth
    participant DB as Database

    User->>Browser: Click "Sign in with Google"
    Browser->>Server: Init OAuth (/api/auth/sign-in/social)
    Note right of Server: PKCE prevents code interception
    Server->>Server: Generate PKCE Challenge
    Server-->>Browser: Redirect to Google Auth URL
    Browser->>Google: Request Authorization
    Google->>User: Show Consent Screen
    User->>Google: Approve
    Google-->>Browser: Redirect with Auth Code
    Browser->>Server: Auth Callback (/api/auth/callback)
    Server->>Server: Verify State
    Server->>Google: Exchange Code for Token
    Google-->>Server: Return Access & ID Tokens
    Server->>Google: Request User Info
    Google-->>Server: Return Profile Data
    Server->>DB: Upsert User Profile
    Server->>DB: Save OAuth Account
    Server->>DB: Create Session
    Note right of Server: HttpOnly cookie secures session
    Server-->>Browser: Set Session Cookie & Redirect
    Browser->>Browser: Check Onboarding Status
    Browser->>User: Show Feed or Onboarding
